OL,3,CGP surgery manager who stole #320,000
OL,4,Cordered to pay back #44,000
OL,6,FThe manager of a busy doctors' surgery
OL,7,Fwho systematically stole almost a
OL,8,Fthird of a million pounds from the
OL,9,Fbusiness has been ordered to pay back
OL,10,F#44,000 of her ill-gotten gains.
OL,12,FClare Boland used her trusted role in
OL,13,Fcharge of finances to pay herself
OL,14,Fthousands of pounds a month on top of
OL,15,Fher #53,000 annual salary.
OL,17,FThe defendant was the practice manager
OL,18,Fof the Fairfield surgery in Port
OL,19,FTalbot, a GP centre with more than 800
OL,20,Fpatients on its books when she fleeced
OL,21,Fthe business over a four-year period.
