OL,6,FSwansea Crown Court has previously
OL,7,Fheard that Boland's role meant she had
OL,8,Fsole responsibility for the surgery's
OL,9,Ffinances including organising payments
OL,10,Fto doctors and staff and paying bills
OL,11,Fand expenses.
OL,13,FShe used that position to set up
OL,14,Fregular monthly payments in the name
OL,15,Fof a real medic who had previously
OL,16,Fdone some locum work at the practice.
OL,17,FIn fact the money was going straight
OL,18,Finto a Co-op bank account controlled
OL,19,Fby the defendant.
