OL,6,FThe court heard the fraud only came to
OL,7,Flight in February 2022 when one of the
OL,8,Fdoctors at the surgery happened to see
OL,9,Fa document which set out staff
OL,10,Fpayments and noticed a payment of
OL,11,F#9,000 to a doctor who had worked as a
OL,12,Fone-day-a-week locum at the surgery
OL,13,Fsome years previously.
