OL,6,FBy the time the theft came to light,
OL,7,Fthe defendant had pocketed a total of
OL,8,F#324,706. In March this year Boland,
OL,9,Fof Shelone Road, Briton Ferry, was
OL,10,Fjailed for three years after pleading
OL,11,Fguilty to fraud by abuse of position.
OL,12,FThe court heard the theft had a
OL,13,Fsignificant impact on the surgery and
OL,14,Fleft staff "devastated" and fearing
OL,15,Ffor their jobs.
