OL,6,FThe case returned to court his week
OL,7,Ffollowing a financial investigation
OL,8,Funder Proceeds of Crime Act powers.
OL,9,FThe court heard it was agreed Boland
OL,10,Fhad benefited from her criminal
OL,11,Fconduct to the tune of #389,732.
OL,13,FJudge Catherine Richards made a
OL,14,Fconfiscation order in the available
OL,15,Fsum, which must be paid in three
OL,16,Fmonths with a period of six months in
OL,17,Fprison if the money isn't paid.
